    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in a few areas. The engine and transmission are functional and the car drives well, but you can expect some minor oil seepage and suspension noise over bumps. Visually, the exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and a few non-functional plastic trim pieces. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind doing a little bit of cosmetic or minor mechanical refreshing.",
      "price": 19500.0,
