    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between a reliable daily driver and a pride-of-ownership machine. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front valence and a faint surface scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a clean, smoke-free environment. The premium upholstery is supple, with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule; the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm and quiet over bumps. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide confident, linear stopping power. I have kept a comprehensive folder of service receipts to provide the next owner with complete peace of mind. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a sophisticated balance of performance and value. Meticulously maintained and presenting in excellent mechanical order, it offers the discerning driver a dependable and refined experience. A testament to its previous ownership, this unit stands ready for its next chapter with confidence. Inspections are welcomed to confirm its impressive standard of care.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
