      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left to give! It runs smoothly, looks great, and has been super dependable for all my trips. It\u2019s not brand new, but it\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure with you. I\u2019m looking for a nice, easy sale, so feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
