    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is prioritized with documented rod bearing service and refreshed throttle actuators. The chassis retains its precision via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock for optimal lateral grip. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust and track-ready. A true driver\u2019s spec for those valuing mechanical purity and engineering excellence.",
